======== End 32-bit MinGW only ========
======== 64-bit MinGW only ========

The dll path for libgfortran-3 is broken, so copy the dlls to somewhere more useful
cp /mingw/x86_64-w64-mingw32/lib/*.dll /usr/local/bin

======== End 64-bit MinGW only ========

